2 May 2012Members of the media are advised that the post-Cabinet media briefing by Cabinet Spokesperson and GCIS CEO, Jimmy Manyi will be held on Friday, 4 May 2012 at 09h00 not 10h00 as announced earlier. The venue has also changed to Room 153, Union Buildings. The Cabinet Spokesperson will be joined by the Minister of Sport and Recreation SA, Fikile Mbalula.The full details are as follows: Date: Friday, 4 May 2012 Time: 09h00 Venue: Room 153, Union Buildings, PretoriaNB: There will be a video-link to Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town RSVP: Proffesor Ndawonde proffesor@gcis.gov.za Cell: 078 456 5738 (Pretoria) or Sbongile Dalasile sbongile@gcis.gov.za Cell: 071 292 1006 (Cape Town)Issued by Government Communication and Information System